The closure of the six embassies was announced late last
Thursday as U.S. intelligence has got informations that Osama bin
Laden, an exiled Saudi millionaire suspected of bombing two U.S.
embassies in Africa last year, was in final stage of planning new
attacks against U.S. embassies in the continent. 
