Cooperation (SAARC), the president is also scheduled to visit the
Kathmandu-based SAARC Secretariat, the secretariat said.
</P>
<P>
SAARC was formed in December 1985 to promote cooperation in the
agreed areas among its member states -- Bhutan, Bangladesh, India,
the Maldives, Nepal, Pakistan and Sri Lanka.
</P>
<P>
