<HEADLINE> Egyptian President Plans to Meet Israeli New </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CAIRO, June 29 (Xinhua) -- President Hosni Mubarak would meet
Israeli Prime Minister-elect Ehud Barak as soon as Barak forms his
coalition government.
