<HEADLINE> Shanghai Stock Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 29 (Xinhua) -- The Composite Stock Index on the
Shanghai Stock Exchange finished at 1,739.20 points today, up 46.
