The meetings will be held prior to the 36th plenary session of
the Sino-Portuguese Joint Liaison Group scheduled to start in
Lisbon on July 13.
</P>
<P>
The session will be the last to be held before the handover of
the rule of Macao from Portugal to China on December 20 this year.
