that the mutually beneficial relations between China and Venezuela
will provide development opportunities for both countries.
</P>
<P>
China, which has become Asia's largest investor in Venezuela,
is expected to triple its investment in the country's petroleum
industry, which has already attracted a total of 300 million U.S.
dollars of Chinese investments, he said. 
