AUCKLAND, New Zealand -- Trade ministers or their
representatives of all 21 economies of the Asia Pacific Economic
Cooperation (APEC) are gathering in Auckland, the biggest city of
New Zealand, for a two-day meeting to address key trade issues
facing APEC.
</P>
<P>
